\cf0 This is the GM release of the AppleFWAudio software for Tiger that contains a new streaming engine for all devices and version 7.0 of the FWAUserLib framework. It is a universal binary and works on Tiger based system releases (10.4.x)  This release is intended for hardware device developers to test with the next version of the driver and API and make sure their devices are compatible going forward.\
